'''Stavros''' ({{Lang-el|Σταυρός}}, ''Stavrós'') is a village of the [[Grevena|Grevena municipality]].<ref name="census11"/> Before the 2011 local government reform it was a part of the municipality of [[Theodoros Ziakas (municipality)|Theodoros Ziakas]].<ref name=Kallikratis>[http://www.kedke.gr/uploads2010/FEKB129211082010_kallikratis.pdf Kallikratis law] Greece Ministry of Interior {{el icon}}</ref> The 2011 census recorded 52 residents in the village.<ref name="census11"/> Stavros is a part of the community of [[Mavranaioi]].<ref name="census11"/>

